Wikidata Property (P code) meta: /dummy value - known test or sample values for identifier or scheme/
/root - part of word that does not have a prefix or a suffix/
/trading name - alternative name under which an entity legally trades	/
/caliber - 	inner diameter of the gun barrel for a weapon/
/implementation of a standard, program, specification or programming language/
/conscription number - number identifying a building in one cadastral area/village/neighborhood/
/number of records - number of values of an identifier or records in a catalog/
/item for this sense - concept corresponding to this sense of a lexeme. Do not use on items or properties/
